# CW Node Helper — Config + Doctor demo
# Record: cd ~/dev/cw-node-helper && vhs assets/tapes/config.tape
Output assets/config.gif
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set FontSize 13
Set FontFamily "SF Mono"
Set Theme "Builtin Dark"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Type "cwhelper config"
Enter
Sleep 4s
Type "cwhelper doctor"
Enter
Sleep 4s
